ross you were discussing just now.<br><br>Do as you please, I offered you an olive branch snap it in two if you like, want those interview’s? Want editorials being discussed in Funcom meetings? Want to ‘do it for the people’ I will help ya, slap it back if you like but that’s called cutting your nose off to spite your face. See that as looking down on you if you want, personally I see it as me offering someone a larger audience and a chance to get what he wanted even after insulting me on several occasions, dig it 'kid'. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/udragonflyao.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dragonfly AO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tiny Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#660000>(12/10/01 5:03:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=47.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Oh god no, another fansite pissing match</span><hr size=1> sion , i just went through all 213 of your news topics and guess how many i found that singled out a single player and basically flamed him on the front page? 0. the only two items i found that even came close was one where u made a wise crack at capt fallout . it wasnt that bad of a comment which is a surprise to me considering the flame wars he has started at ao basher. the other i found was a discussion inspired by someone who admitted in the forums that he tried to ebay crap . and that wasnt even a flame of him more of a thing about ebaying and ao in general. i did however find an interesting statement of yours however that i will quote. <br><br><br>&quot;He was stood helpless, he had no health left, and no equipment to defend himself, I blasted him and watched his body fall to the ground, a smile on my face I typed a short line of choice words and carried on